Privacy Policy
Information we collect
Optional DetailsPro Community accounts, if opted into to share designs with the community, are created securely with Sign In with Apple. We store information about the designs DetailsPro Community users choose to share with the community. We also collect anonymous, aggregate statistics about which community designs are most popular.
Technical basics
DetailsPro syncs files securely through iCloud only. Your designs, media, and other data stay within your iCloud account and never leave your iCloud account, unless you optionally use DetailsPro Community by creating a profile and then manually uploading designs. If you upload a design to the DetailsPro Community after optionally creating a DetailsPro Community profile, we must store the design to make it available for download by others.
Analytics
DetailsPro collects aggregate, anonymous statistics, such as how many users use a particular feature, to improve the app.
Information usage
We use the information we collect to operate and improve our website, apps, and customer support.
We do not share any information with outside parties except to the extent necessary to accomplish
DetailsPro's
functionality. In the future, we may sell to, buy, merge with, or partner with other businesses. In such transactions, user information may be among the transferred assets.
Contacting Us
If you have questions regarding this privacy policy, you may email
